\paragraph{Dynamic Latent Dimension.}
We utilize MMPPL to guide the dimension setting of visual latent variables, while also using PPL as a reference. Table~\ref{tab:ablation_latent} demonstrates the impact of different dimension settings on transfer performance. We use the average number of dimensions for the KV cache per token to represent the space overhead.
