Under the dynamic setting, layer-wise ranks selected by MMPPL yield a more compact per-layer configuration.
Despite reducing the overall average cache dimension compared to the mean-512 baseline (530 vs.\ 576), PPL further decreases (11.23 vs.\ 11.66) and MMPPL improves (3.61 vs.\ 4.03).
